{"id":97,"count":2,"description":"Explore Andaman \u2013 A tropical paradise in the Bay of Bengal, the Andaman Islands are famous for their crystal-clear waters, white sandy beaches, and vibrant marine life. From the historical Cellular Jail in Port Blair to the turquoise beauty of Havelock Island\u2019s Radhanagar Beach and the coral wonders of Neil Island, Andaman is a perfect mix of history, adventure, and relaxation. Visitors can enjoy snorkeling, scuba diving, glass-bottom boat rides, and water sports, or simply relax by the serene shores. With lush forests, exotic wildlife, and breathtaking sunsets, Andaman offers a rejuvenating escape for beach lovers, honeymooners, and adventure seekers alike.","link":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/destinations\/explore-andaman\/","name":"EXPLORE ANDAMAN","slug":"explore-andaman","taxonomy":"destination","parent":0,"meta":[],"thumbnail":{"width":900,"height":596,"file":"2025\/09\/EXPLORE-ANDAMAN.png","filesize":1109344,"sizes":{"medium":{"file":"EXPLORE-ANDAMAN-300x199.png","width":300,"height":199,"filesize":89354,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/EXPLORE-ANDAMAN-300x199.png"},"thumbnail":{"file":"EXPLORE-ANDAMAN-150x150.png","width":150,"height":150,"filesize":38100,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/EXPLORE-ANDAMAN-150x150.png"},"medium_large":{"file":"EXPLORE-ANDAMAN-768x509.png","width":768,"height":509,"filesize":507195,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/EXPLORE-ANDAMAN-768x509.png"},"trip-thumb-size":{"file":"EXPLORE-ANDAMAN-374x226.png","width":374,"height":226,"filesize":119405,"mime_type":"image\/png","source_url":"https:\/\/realtrips.thefuturecity.in\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/09\/EXPLORE-ANDAMAN-374x226.png"},"destination-thumb-size":{"file":"EXPLORE-ANDAMAN-600x596.png","width":600,"heig